{"tid":2333390,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【陷5角苦戀】陳卓賢感情生活亂晒龍！中墨混血索模加入混戰","createTime":"2020-12-20T11:01:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-20T13:06:41.000Z","uid":312363,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"338712ec6476307501f8885c0be57de3b69f09b0","tid":2333390,"uid":312363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T11:01:31.000Z","msg":"組合MIRROR成員陳卓賢（Ian）被東網踢爆秘撻前港姐冠軍陳曉華，之後再爆出陳曉華原來跟狄以達餘情未了，繼而再爆Ian跟余潔滢戲假情真。原本已複雜的關係未算亂，有指Ian的真女友另有其人，正是藝人朱鑑然前女友、中墨西哥混血女模盧慧敏（Amy Lo），如今變成5角苦戀，網友等埋位食花生。<br />\n<br />\nAmy與Ian因拍ViuTV劇集《無限斜棟有限公司》而結緣，更在劇中奪去Ian的螢幕初吻，疑錫出真愛，之後Amy都有客串拍《男排女將》，連續兩劇合作，名正言順做跟得女友。<br />\n<br />\n與Ian同齡也是27歲的Amy，是余文樂的御用模特兒，最為人認識是她與朱鑑然拍拖時，傳出兩人訂婚的消息，但朱鑑然經理人否認其事，並透露兩人早在去年已分手。東網致電朱鑑然，問到Amy暗交Ian一事，他說：「多謝關心，依家係朋友關係！」<br />\n<br />\n<strong>東網唔貼link</strong>"},{"pid":"7b8c2e89d9ac6d2a7a396dcbd858c7e3b7b97fe1","tid":2333390,"uid":26001,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T11:02:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7d6a910c9665d10a19e513be5846b11a00b0935","tid":2333390,"uid":24457,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T11:05:59.000Z","msg":"就嚟可以開多季追星出嚟"},{"pid":"a4f65f816bee6e35df07d8c2a035206080db0006","tid":2333390,"uid":67840,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T11:06:04.000Z","msg":"抵死，最憎 ian"},{"pid":"09394235e07fd3388764e2afb2b37de3d5783a4b","tid":2333390,"uid":228223,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T11:17:55.000Z","msg":"Ian肯定好撚鍾意高妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"576a79ef0a9aa74f676db7b2e9036cd89965bace","tid":2333390,"uid":215861,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"cit